Description: ENHANCED FLEECE TACTICAL JACKET - OD - L

Chest pockets- dual vertical chest pockets keep gear secure and safe. Sleeve pockets- dual zippered sleeve pockets keep gear accessible. High collar- 3 3/4" collar provides superior neck protection in windy or wet conditions. Full zip entry- neck to waist dual zippers w/ nylon pull tabs which adjust to changing weather conditions. Slash pockets- deep  verticle zippered pockets have great capacity. Adjustable cuffs- hook & loop closures & sleeve extension w/ thumb hole. Corded bottom- fully adjustable elastic w/ quick locks assure a snug  custom fit. Bonus: includes: name  rank & branch loop strips
